Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{radio}{\a6\i1}And now, news about the incident at True Cross Academy.{\i0}{maybe a6 the radio broadcast lines, what do you think Zwill?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{radio}{\a6\i1}The students who were taken hostage were all rescued uninjured, but the culprit escaped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{radio}{\a6\i1}The Order of the True Cross is conducting a search within a 10 km radius, but so far without success.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi! Please infuse the valeriana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.28,0:00:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're all right at the Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have terrible wounds! They must be treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move her! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that boys take after their mothers, and you really resemble Yuri a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Fujimoto tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only photo of Yuri I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimoto named Sir Pheles your guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Sir Pheles has been arrested by the Order of the True Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to take you in as your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In kindergarten, we had to draw portraits on Mother's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin drew it from imagination, but I couldn't draw anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm feeling just like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize for making you feel like that for the past 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was confined all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confined?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything in the catastrophe of the Blue Night 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My position, my honor, even my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my only beloved daughter, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Mother was killed by Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Satan didn't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Vatican, who also confined me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, when Satan slaughtered countless Exorcists,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri of all conceived the children of a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother and I, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grigori burnt Yuri as a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There are no witch hunts anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Mother judged?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the authority of the Order of the True Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sacrificed Yuri to achieve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ways of the leaders haven't changed in the past 600 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They confined me, since I'm the father of a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already lost all my will to live. My only hope was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The photo Fujimoto gave to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had it with me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hug the children Yuri died giving birth to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if your existence was revealed, the Vatican wouldn't stay silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you couldn't come for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now there is no more danger from the Grigori.{i'm not sure if it's the grigori in danger or that they're dangerous}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling this only to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly the arrangements to take in Rin are not ready, because he awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take in? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragoon Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A factory of anti-demon weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the True Cross has turned into Mephisto's puppet. They can't protect Assiah anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join me, Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of peace and the future of humanity, let us start a new age.{I hate fuckers like this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the monastery?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to his flames, we could get rid of most of the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Professor Neuhaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being questioned in the Great Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have the right to listen, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Professor Neuhaus is on the Vatican's wanted list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even our Principal was arrested... What's going to happen to the Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already. She is my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that web clearly originates from Gehenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me your wife was possessed{overtaken} by a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell us so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That your beloved family was killed by Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would dead people walk around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she attacking my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You quickened her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a technique to bring back the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember telling you that in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked as the head of an artificial life research facility in Poland.{wasn't that research banned for 300 years? -sekrit labs need no permissions}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used that technology and resurrected your dead wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did deep freeze and preserve her corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't revive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cross that line, the Gates of Heaven will close forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got back to the facility, her hibernation capsule was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!{might want to turn it into the polish equivalent}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that a demon had possessed the corpse of my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't make my beloved Michelle suffer death again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igor Neuhaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are arrested for artificial life research and performing quickening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn down this impure institution!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Michelle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the keys, I escaped to Japan with Michelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since then she's been changing little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot! Someone... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably remembers that she was burnt to death by blue flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must die... everyone connected to Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slaughter them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle turned into a vengeful demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to bring her back while I still could, but you know the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you just tell us about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had told you, there's nothing you could do to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's possessed by a demon, but she's nothing but a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within a few days, she will begin to rot and return to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it? I'm going after his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what if you find her? What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But I can't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots must go forward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My familiars are already after her. This seal will lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You oughta show some respect. Now get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you find her, report back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try anything alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But who the hell could have revived Neuhaus' wife?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in such a hurry I didn't think about it, but how do I use this again?{I ran out so enthusiastically, but how do I use this again?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call and ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a total idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, I'd be so dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yea, it's Okumura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,You shouldn't move around yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,But I'm glad you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,Where am I? Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,You collapsed in our garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,He helped me to carry you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become an Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll show me the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? This wasn't here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shura's familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the secret garden of my granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always told me that if we listened to what the plants have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll bloom beautifully. It's really true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny could hear them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many spirits loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry... I'm just babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like the Garden of Amahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband told me about it, it's the garden with all the flowers God created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it really existed, I'm sure it'd be something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Please be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've met someone who knows about the Garden of Amahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shiemi Moriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Michelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiemi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd be in Satan's league too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that this is revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My reason to live turned to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By your blue flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how Satan took everything from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take everything important from...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! She's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless. She's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She returned to life to take revenge on Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way, Shiemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! She's not a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to kill Suguro and everyone in our monastery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must protect those important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! If she was really a bad person, the Green Men wouldn't help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Professor Neuhaus' wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, it won't connect?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta make a call, stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hullo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rin? What's up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really? Where?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Exorcist Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Why would she go there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I'll take Neuhaus there, so don't let her out of your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come. Or rather, it's best you don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What's wrong, Rin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did something happen? Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This beauty doesn't fit a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Auguste! We have apprehended the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You demon, who took the face of a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reviving the dead is the greatest taboo in Assiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will eliminate you in the name of the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take responsibility for all of her sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I beg you, please let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful bond of marriage you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... The only time the dead may return is when
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the angels blow the trumpets of the last Rapture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll protect a demon, son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't like how you're turning Shiemi's home upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you oppose me, you oppose the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's got nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Satan's son is fighting to help me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tried to take away everything important to him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all you can do, son of Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SHUT THE FUCK UP!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Snakefang!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Shura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!{calm yo tits lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do if you lose control?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way, Shura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what you're trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shot her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Rin}{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Garden of Amahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paradise where all the flowers of the world are gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't it, but I'm sure it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where we can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look for it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest those heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many Green Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Auguste...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the bells ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent summons from the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent summons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can find it for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Garden of Amahara where they can live in peace together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arthur Auguste Angel reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Paladin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the Grigori?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! The Grigori are the highest authority of the Order of the True Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}were{\i0\fscx140} {\r}the highest authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today I, Ernest Frederick Aegin, take on their duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen! Our order has been fighting a defensive war for all of our recorded history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to take the offensive has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will eliminate all the demons and bring peace to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio Okumura...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, is this what Exorcists do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:23:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said let go!
