Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{English}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:26.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark side in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:29.28,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the unerasable sadness of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:31.49,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright if I don't really mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.24,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}so I fire my blasters and stretch out my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:39.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,230)}Since when has my way been unavoidable like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:43.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,400)}And now there's no one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.42,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:49.05,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cry for my pride, I can't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}An aria of love resounding through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,this distorted reality of twisted prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams and tomorrow are collapsing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:02.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,230)}because throwing away the lies would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.82,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}Good bye precious life.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.53,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Go and repaint this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.28,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,try it for your pride, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.41,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I sing the song of love and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,let its wish reach through this distorted world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,to build our bonds and the tomorrow to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:22.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}Throwing away the lies was important after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}because this is my precious life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:29.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark cloud in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,disappearing and light is shining on the road I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:34.39,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight, there's no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:38.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,820)}I brandished my two-edged sword.
