Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:37.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(270,0)}I'm lightly fluttering in wondrous light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.96,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,440)}like a dancing butterfly in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.96,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(270,500)}Is this place in another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:50.84,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(140,820)}My fall isn't slowing down so
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.63,0:21:53.89,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(220,480)}cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.10,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.85,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The numbers that make my head spin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:00.68,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,230)}are forming a rising spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:04.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:07.98,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:11.49,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:19.62,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:24.83,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:27.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.51,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.80,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:34.59,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}wired life.
